# Worker Command Center 

It shall be called SuperVisor

This is a piece of Software, based on node.js and mongoDB.
It allows full Control over a net of workers.

The Database holds the workers with their config, the gui allows to enter them manually.
Also you may enter an intercoma and use this to get workers from this one.

The Gui allows to
- Get the Status
- Reconfigure
- Show the Topographs
- Stop, Start, Restart Workers
- Try to get a Worker by using "identify" on an ip and port